nodes.text: A species of squid was found on the estuary moon of Trask. The species was used to make chowder Around 9 ABY, Grogu was served a bowl of chowder containing a live specimen. The creature latched onto Grogu's face until the Mandalorian Din Djarin pried it off with his knife. One was later consumed alive by the Mandalorian Koska Reeves.
